sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant View as Meeting Form
    participant Controller as MeetingNoteController
    participant Model as MeetingNote Model
    participant Anggota as Anggota Model

    Admin->>View: Buka Form Buat Notulensi
    View->>Controller: GET /create
    Controller->>Model: generateDocumentNo()
    Model-->>Controller: Return "0005" (Auto Increment)
    Controller->>Anggota: Get List Anggota
    Anggota-->>Controller: Return List
    Controller-->>View: Show Form with Doc No & Options

    Admin->>View: Submit Data (Attendance Multi-select)
    View->>Controller: POST /store
    Controller->>Controller: Implode Attendance Array to String
    Controller->>Model: Create()
    Model-->>Controller: Success
    Controller-->>View: Redirect Success

    Admin->>View: Lihat Ranking
    View->>Controller: GET /ranking
    Controller->>Model: Get All Meetings
    loop Calculate Attendance
        Controller->>Controller: Parse Comma Separated Attendance
        Controller->>Controller: Count Frequency per Anggota
    end
    Controller->>Anggota: Match Names to Anggota Data
    Controller-->>View: Show Leaderboard
